com.bitplan.expr

Class NumexprBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bitplan.expr.NumexprBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NumexprListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class NumexprBaseListener
extends Object
implements NumexprListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of NumexprListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
